<section class="contact" aria-label="Contacto">
    <div class="contact-inner">
        <h2>Reservá tu turno</h2>
        <p>¿Listo para un corte nuevo? Reservá en línea o llamanos y te asesoramos.</p>
        <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/turnos">Reservar turno</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/contacto">Contactar</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .contact { 
        padding: 64px 20px; 
        background: var(--color-bg); 
        color: var(--color-text); 
    }

    .contact-inner { 
        max-width: 1000px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
        text-align: center; 
    }
    
    .contact-inner h2 { 
        font-size: 1.8rem; 
        margin-bottom: 8px; 
    }

    .contact-inner p { 
        color: var(--color-text-light); 
        margin-bottom: 18px; 
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .actions { 
        display: flex; 
        gap: 12px; 
        justify-content:center; 
    }

    .btn { 
        padding: 12px 20px; 
        border-radius: 28px; 
        font-weight: 700; 
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn.primary { 
        background: var(--color-accent); 
        color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    }

    .btn.primary:hover { 
        background: var(--color-text-light);
        color: var(--color-white);
    }

    .btn.ghost { 
        background: transparent; 
        border: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); 
        color: var(--color-text); 
    }

    .btn.ghost:hover { 
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03); 
    }
</style>
